50|$|An NRENum.net Registry is {{an entity}} that is {{authorised}} by the NRENum.net Operations Team {{to operate the}} national or regional Tier-1 <b>Domain</b> <b>Name</b> <b>Server</b> and {{be responsible for the}} county code(s) delegated. In many countries there is a National Research and Education Networking organisation (NREN) that acts as the Registry of the country.|$|E
